Classes in book used by book
ProductBook
          The ProductBook object maintains the Buy and Sell sides of a stock’s “book”.
ProductBookSide
          Maintains the content of one side (Buy or Sell) of a Stock (product) “book”.
ProductBookSide.BookSide
          Hold valid values for the side that the current ProductBookSide represents.
ProductService
          This class is the Facade to the entities that make up the Products (Stocks), and the Product Books (“booked” tradables on the Buy and Sell side).
TradeProcessor
          Interface that defines the functionality needed to “execute” the actual trades between Tradable objects in this book side.
TradeProcessor.AllocationStrategy
          Trades will be executed based on their price and the time they were submitted to they system.
